sc_cat_item.description:
• 2 (5-ounce) cans tuna
  • ¼ cup mayonnaise
  • 1 stalk of celery, diced
  • 2 tablespoons red onion, diced
  • 1-2 tablespoons chopped parsley, chives and/or other herbs
  • ½ tablespoon Dijon mustard
  • salt and pepper, to taste

* One quantity is equal to four servings.
sc_cat_item.name: Tuna Salad
sc_cat_item.short_description: You really can’t beat a classic tuna salad.
